Subclasses of Subscription in org.cougaar.core.blackboard
 class CollectionSubscription<E>
          A subclass of Subscription that maintains a Collection of blackboard objects matching the filter predicate, plus ChangeReports for the objects changed since the last transaction.
 class DeltaSubscription
          A subscription that only tracks add/change/remove deltas.
 class EnvelopeMetricsSubscription
          A Subscription that collects EnvelopeMetrics.
 class IncrementalSubscription<E>
          A CollectionSubscription that records add/change/remove deltas.
 class PublisherSubscription
          A subscription that tracks the plugin publisher and add/change stacks for UniqueObjects.
 class QuerySubscription<E>
          A lightweight CollectionSubscription used to take a single "query" snapshot of the blackboard.
 class TimestampSubscription
          A Subscription that tracks UniqueObject publishAdd and most recent publishChange timestamps.
 class TodoSubscription<E>
          A subscription that queues objects, such as Alarms and other non-blackboard callbacks, for processing in the plugin's "execute()" thread.
